          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-accent text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6">
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-3">获得批准</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            24小时内获得批准。我们将为您提供最佳的融资条款。
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-3xl font-bold mx-auto mb-6">
            4
