            简单的文件要求，快速处理
          </p>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-accent mx-auto mt-4"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center">
